_sText:
Took me 12 hours to get this far.
i am done, except for different versions, 

gg_  will be coming next.

aim_  will be coming after that.


There are 2 bomb sites, both are a serious challenge to secure.
Great flow and vertical attack points, multiple paths 
to get to where your going. Each battle has a tonne of 
excitement. 

Remember the 2 hidden stashes placed strategically, 
help you when your in need of some edge. 

i personally didn't like  the 2 textures approach to a map
so i added some masks, natural lighting, and light effects.
i hope the architexture is enjoyable. the frates on mine were 
still great, 60+

of course they go down the more peeps get on... but i comfortably ran 29 peeps, with minimal pc slowage.

P4 3000mhz, 128 sapphire vid card 9600 1gig ram

please rate this map...
please post comments...
please say no to greenhouse emissions!!!
